{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100170/extras/2.jpg?t=1666816580\" /><br>NO WAY OUT is a first person psychological horror game, featuring scary and jumpy gameplay and an unsettling and interesting narrative.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORYLINE</h2></h2>There is now 2 possibilities for a Narrative, maybe more that one ending?<br><br>You were driving around and you got lost without signal and No Way of getting Out of the place where you stopped. The only solution is to keep going on foot until you find a place to get away for the rain and thunderstorm. The thing you didn't know is that the house you get into, may not allow you to get out! You start by finding a way into the house, but at the end your main goal is to find Way Out of the house also keeping in mind that you may have NO WAY OUT.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHARACTERS</h2></h2>You are the main character in the story, other characters narrative is told by papers found in the map or audios/videos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2></h2>Use everything that you can to survive this scary story and dive deeper into it.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100170/extras/1.jpg?t=1666816580\" /><br><br>Develop the photos that you take to find clues or discover more about the narrative.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100170/extras/3.jpg?t=1666816580\" /><br><br>Unlock door by searching for the key or by solving puzzels.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100170/extras/4.jpg?t=1666816580\" /><br><br>Use all your equipment to enjoy this terrifying experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100170/extras/5.jpg?t=1666816580\" /><br><